安装

# 如果没有~/.fonts目录，则先主动建立

$ mkdir ~/.fonts

$ mv monaco.ttf ~/.fonts

$ mkfontscale
$ mkfontdir
$ fc-cache -fv ~/.fonts

/home/scuter/.fonts: caching, new cache contents: 1 fonts, 0 dirs
/var/cache/fontconfig: not cleaning unwritable cache directory
/home/scuter/.fontconfig: cleaning cache directory
fc-cache: succeeded


